in west hollywood,

00:13.314 --> 00:16.515
and paige young was the girl

00:16.617 --> 00:19.785
that lived behind me
in the carriage house.

00:19.887 --> 00:21.854
She was literally
the girl next door.

00:21.956 --> 00:26.558
Paige was an artist and a--
and a pretty good one.

00:26.660 --> 00:30.629
She had her own artistic vision.

00:30.731 --> 00:33.866
She was also
a "playboy" centerfold.

00:33.968 --> 00:36.935
And I remember the day
she said to me

00:37.038 --> 00:39.605
