01:26.754 --> 01:29.388
and I-I remember
sitting on the bed,

01:29.490 --> 01:32.191
and I called the police.

01:32.293 --> 01:36.161
In two days, everything
was cleaned out and gone.

01:36.263 --> 01:38.130
